paragraphs.text:
//5. Show the number of items reviewed by each user in the newly-created u_data table.
sqlContext.sql("select userid, count(movieid) as number_movies from u_data group by userid order by number_movies").show

//6. Show the number of users that reviewed each item in the newly created u_data table.
sqlContext.sql("select movieid, count(userid) as number_users from u_data group by movieid order by number_users desc").show
